{"title":"[USACO 1.5] 数字金字塔","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":128,"url":"http://cogs.pro:8080/cogs/problem/problem.php?pid=pJiSSyWja","statement":[{"title":"# 题目描述","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h2 style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-weight:normal;margin-left:0px;font-size:19px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:18px;\">描述  USACO 1.5.1</span> \n</h2>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">观察下面的数字金字塔。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">写一个程序来查找从最高点到底部任意处结束的路径，使路径经过数字的和最大。每一步可以走到左下方的点也可以到达右下方的点。</span> \n</p>\n<pre>         7 \n      3   8 \n    8   1   0 \n  2   7   4   4 \n4   5   2   6   5 \n</pre>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">在上面的样例中,从7 到 3 到 8 到 7 到 5 的路径产生了最大</span> \n</p>\n<h2 style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-weight:normal;margin-left:0px;font-size:19px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\"><br/>\n格式</span> \n</h2>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">PROGRAM NAME</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">: numtri</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">INPUT FORMAT</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">:</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">(file numtri.in)</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">第一个行包含 R(1&lt;= R&lt;=1000) ,表示行的数目。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">后面每行为这个数字金字塔特定行包含的整数。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">所有的被供应的整数是非负的且不大于100。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">OUTPUT FORMAT</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">:</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">(file numtri.out)</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\">单独的一行,包含那个可能得到的最大的和。</span> \n</p>\n<h2 style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-weight:normal;margin-left:0px;font-size:19px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\"><br/>\nSAMPLE INPUT</span> \n</h2>\n<pre>5\n7\n3 8\n8 1 0\n2 7 4 4\n4 5 2 6 5 \n</pre>\n<h2 style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-weight:normal;margin-left:0px;font-size:19px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size:16px;\"><br/>\nSAMPLE OUTPUT</span> \n</h2>\n<pre>30</pre>\n\n"}]}